edu.harvard.integer.service.persistance

Class PersistenceManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.harvard.integer.service.BaseManager
      • edu.harvard.integer.service.persistance.PersistenceManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BaseManagerInterface, PersistenceManagerInterface

    public class PersistenceManager
extends BaseManager
implements PersistenceManagerInterface
    The PersistenceManager is responsible for creating DAO's. The DAO's returned may or may not be newly created. The DAO's should not store any local variables since the DAO can be reused. Each DAO has its own get method. The method has the name of get. The DAOs all are named DAO.
